VISUALFORCE B2B COMMERCE
User Interface

Manage settings for your storefront's user experience, search engine optimization (SEO), and static resources that contain media files for your storefront. The User Interface module's API name is ui.

Bot Breadcrumb Template
CONSIDERATION	VALUE
API Name	ui.bothomepagetmpl
Externally Safe?	
Usage	Override the Default Bot-Enabled Pages or Components
Compatibility	B2B Commerce for Visualforce Summer ’19 (version 4.11) or later
Bot Category Tree Template
CONSIDERATION	VALUE
API Name	ui.botcategorytreetmpl
Externally Safe?	
Usage	Override the Default Bot-Enabled Pages or Components
Compatibility	B2B Commerce for Visualforce Summer ’19 (version 4.11) or later

CONSIDERATION	VALUE

CONSIDERATION	VALUE

Bot User Agent n
CONSIDERATION	VALUE
API Name	ui.botuaren
Externally Safe?	
Usage	Serve Bot-Enabled Versions of Storefront Pages
Compatibility	B2B Commerce for Visualforce Summer ’18 (version 4.9) or later
Desktop Template
CONSIDERATION	VALUE
API Name	ui.desktoptmpl
Externally Safe?	
Usage	Create a Gross Layout Override
Compatibility	B2B Commerce for Visualforce Summer ’18 (version 4.9) or later
Enable Canonical and Alternate Language Links
CONSIDERATION	VALUE
API Name	ui.canonicalaltlinks
Externally Safe?	
Usage	Insert Canonical URLs and Alternate Language URLs
Compatibility	B2B Commerce for Visualforce Summer ’19 (version 4.11) or later
Image Static Resource n
CONSIDERATION	VALUE
API Name	ui.isresn
Externally Safe?	
Usage	
Add a Category Image from a Static Resource
Add a Product Image from a Static Resource
Add a Promotion Image from a Static Resource

Compatibility	B2B Commerce for Visualforce Summer ’18 (version 4.9) or later
Lightning Community Sitemap
CONSIDERATION	VALUE
API Name	ui.lightningsitemap
Externally Safe?	
Usage	Specify the Destination for Links to Your Storefront's Home Page
Compatibility	B2B Commerce for Visualforce Winter ’21 (version 4.13) or later
No Image Source
CONSIDERATION	VALUE
API Name	ui.noimage
Externally Safe?	
Usage	The name of the static resource that contains a backup image file you want to show if the intended image doesn't load. Prefix the static resource name with c__ if the resource is from a subscriber org and isn't packaged.
Compatibility	B2B Commerce for Visualforce Summer ’18 (version 4.9) or later
Static Resource Namespaces List
CONSIDERATION	VALUE
API Name	ui.nsList
Externally Safe?	
Usage	Create Metadata for the Namespace List Configuration Added in a Patch
Compatibility	
B2B Commerce for Visualforce Winter ’21 (version 4.13) patch 3.149.9 or later
B2B Commerce for Visualforce Spring ’20 (version 4.12) patch 3.147.14 or later
Override Standard Include
CONSIDERATION	VALUE
API Name	ui.ovrincl
Externally Safe?	
Usage	Exclude the Standard CSS and JavaScript Libraries
Compatibility	B2B Commerce for Visualforce Summer ’18 (version 4.9) or later
Restore Legacy jQuery HTML Prefilter
CONSIDERATION	VALUE
API Name	ui.restorelegacyhtmlprefilter
Externally Safe?	
Usage	
Default JavaScript Libraries for Storefront Pages
(Salesforce Knowledge) Upgrade to jQuery 3.5.1 in B2B Commerce for Visualforce Spring ’20 (Version 4.12) or Earlier

Compatibility	
B2B Commerce for Visualforce Spring ’20 (version 4.12) patch 3.147.5 or later
B2B Commerce for Visualforce Summer ’19 (version 4.11) patch 3.145.20 or later
B2B Commerce for Visualforce Spring ’19 (version 4.10) patch 3.142.26 or later
B2B Commerce for Visualforce Summer ’18 (version 4.9) patch 3.136.38 or later
Template Version
CONSIDERATION	VALUE
API Name	ui.tmplver
Externally Safe?	
Usage	

Default JavaScript Libraries for Storefront Pages

TIP We recommend that new implementations always leave this configuration set to boot3.

Compatibility	B2B Commerce for Visualforce Summer ’18 (version 4.9) or later
Use Bot User-Agent Matching
CONSIDERATION	VALUE
API Name	ui.usebotuare
Externally Safe?	
Usage	Serve Bot-Enabled Versions of Storefront Pages
Compatibility	B2B Commerce for Visualforce Summer ’18 (version 4.9) or later

CONSIDERATION	VALUE
API Name	ui.usefurls
Externally Safe?	
Usage	Serve Friendly URLs for Storefront Pages
Compatibility	B2B Commerce for Visualforce Summer ’18 (version 4.9) or later

CONSIDERATION	VALUE
API Name	ui.usemin
Externally Safe?	
Usage	Default JavaScript Libraries for Storefront Pages
Compatibility	B2B Commerce for Visualforce Summer ’18 (version 4.9) or later
